Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There's more?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-There are 3 more Whitebeard Pirates ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They've infiltrated the bay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.53,0:05:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's the...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.57,0:05:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...1st division commander—Marco!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The 14 commanders...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,they're all here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.65,0:06:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been awhile, Sengoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.92,0:06:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Whitebeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.95,0:06:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You better tell me that my beloved son...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...is all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.31,0:06:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that we let them get this close!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.65,0:06:39.88,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,We made it through the gate...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:45.46,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,but what Vi'm concerned about is whether your guys' father is here or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.52,0:06:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,"Your guys'"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.66,0:06:51.43,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,Vi don't think that Dragon\Nwould let them kill his own son...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my dad and Ace's are not the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:07:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad is Dragon\Nbut Ace's dad is Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.64,0:07:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He got such a great father but he never met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd get mad every time I mentioned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I shouldn't have said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.40,0:07:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a second, Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.61,0:07:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:07:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.36,0:08:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He cracked the air?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.98,0:08:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's that explosion coming from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.21,0:08:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No good! The water surface is too high!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A seaquake! He's distorting the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The other side, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.89,0:08:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the power of Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading out first!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.91,0:08:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.85,0:08:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. See you, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be a lot stronger when I leave here in 3 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll show them how it's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard! He became a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.48,0:09:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pirate ship! I never seen their flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a pirate who's become very powerful rapidly recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,"D?" Where is he from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.49,0:09:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't quite figure that out
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but even as a rookie, he has the power of Logia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a dashing young man in the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He refused the offer to join the Warlords.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How long have they been at this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They're still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.85,0:09:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They shouldn't rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious, Captain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to see him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.89,0:10:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...Red-Haired Shanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Spade Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The infamous super rookie came to say hello to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not what you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother was always talking about you as his lifesaver
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.27,0:10:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,so I came to say thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Luffy's brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.84,0:10:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that he had a brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, I'm glad to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me all about yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a banquet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.29,0:10:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's still talking about becoming the Pirate King?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.69,0:10:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's his favorite phrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.67,0:10:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for him because...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who'll become the next King.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.01,0:10:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I'll let the whole world know the power I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? How'll you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.75,0:11:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,By beating the strongest man in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.38,0:11:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Whitebeard?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, big guy, I wanna see\Nthe guy who goes by Whitebeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.46,0:11:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot introduce a sharp\Nyoung man like you to the old chap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.56,0:11:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, that's Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the Warlord?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.77,0:11:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'd gain prestige if I beat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not on the crew of the Whitebeard Pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.07,0:11:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but I owe him, so I'll fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been 5 days since they started fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.99,0:11:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They're both gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.47,0:12:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.88,0:12:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one of you wants to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.93,0:12:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna fight you as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Whitebeard Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.63,0:12:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna fight you people single-handedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.35,0:12:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Flame Fence!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.55,0:12:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.42,0:12:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Ace, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.26,0:12:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:13:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? Are you backing away after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.70,0:13:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let my crew get way. Instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm staying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.40,0:13:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You snot-nosed brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How cheeky you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the guy who contended for supremacy with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.07,0:13:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.94,0:13:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Still some fight left in you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You are too valuable to let die now, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If you still wanna run wild,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.09,0:14:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,run as wild as you want on the sea under my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.63,0:14:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Become my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.32,0:15:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.19,0:15:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the 4th division commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.16,0:15:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Thatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.73,0:15:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're gonna join us,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,we should become friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.13,0:15:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're grumpy when you wake up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, you wanna know\Nwhat happened after you passed out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Your crew came to get you back
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.58,0:15:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,so we beat the hell out of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're not dead. They're on this ship, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have to put me in cuffs or shackles?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.82,0:15:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Shackles? We don't need them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.08,0:16:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.75,0:16:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what time it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.73,0:16:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, he fell overboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody, help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.14,0:16:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been at it every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.14,0:16:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How gutsy he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.11,0:16:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be more than 100 times now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:16:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...do you people call him Pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.61,0:17:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he calls us "sons."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.08,0:17:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We are all hated by the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So it makes us happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.92,0:17:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's just a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But it still makes us happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna keep doing this after your life has been saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You got to make up your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not capable of killing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's either get off of this ship and start over again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...or stay here and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...wear the Whitebeard logo on your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Doma?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace did it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.47,0:18:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He made Doma and his crew surrender by himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to command 2nd division?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.31,0:18:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a vacant post\Nfor a long time. If you took it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.08,0:18:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...nobody would complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one of the originals, right?\NDon't you mind it at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.99,0:18:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got no such ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.56,0:18:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it for us! Commander Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops, you got a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.13,0:19:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that was surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.81,0:19:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Your character is nothing like Roger's.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.98,0:19:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He was your enemy, right? Don't you wanna kick me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.65,0:19:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that it's important but it's such a small matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.15,0:19:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter who your father is, we are all children of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.47,0:19:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace will be our 2nd division commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.28,0:19:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a star, don't look dazed. Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, the food's not leaving so don't rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.61,0:20:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're the star of this banquet so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He falls asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.98,0:20:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Whitebeard got a powerful newbie again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.65,0:20:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that he's insanely strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.86,0:20:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,2nd division came to cover us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thatch, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.10,0:20:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Your bounty will rise again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.52,0:21:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace, I found something interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.25,0:21:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is it a devil fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.69,0:21:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what fruit it is yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.97,0:21:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Ace, just calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.18,0:21:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops said that this is an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.88,0:21:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to go after Teach!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.45,0:21:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go! I am his commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.12,0:21:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't do anything about it,\NThatch's spirit can't rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.76,0:21:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.89,0:21:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. This is an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.93,0:21:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.30,0:22:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He killed his crewmate and ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.40,0:22:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He had been beholden to you for decades
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.01,0:22:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and then he threw dirt in your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.14,0:22:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And above all, he disgraced my father's name
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.38,0:22:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can't allow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.78,0:22:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! Come back, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.08,0:22:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.78,0:22:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What caused that quake?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.85,0:22:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.09,0:22:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.56,0:22:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I ignored your advice and took off!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.29,0:22:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you just give up on me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.89,0:23:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who caused all of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.57,0:23:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.10,0:23:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who told you to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.84,0:23:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Son.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.49,0:23:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All of the cast has assembled.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.49,0:23:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Whitebeard's tremendous power\Nbrings a huge tsunami
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.56,0:23:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,that threatens to swallow up
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.39,0:23:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,all the brave men of Marineford,\Nas well as the peace and justice there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.23,0:23:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A battle crossing generations begins at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.90,0:23:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.40,0:23:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Force That Could Destroy the World! The Power of the Tremor-Tremor Fruit"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.90,0:23:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
